msgstr "À quoi ça sert"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:128
#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid "Recommended value (MR/MRS)"
msgstr "Valeur recommandée (MR/MRS)"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Active Certificate**"
msgstr "**Certificat actif**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"The eHealth **.p12** certificate that authenticates the institution and "
"signs the SOAP messages. Import it first under *eHealth / Certificates*, "
"then select it here."
msgstr ""
"Le certificat **.p12** eHealth qui authentifie l'institution et signe les "
"messages SOAP. Importez-le d'abord sous *eHealth / Certificats*, puis "
"sélectionnez-le ici."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"**Your establishment's** certificate, obtained from **ehealth.fgov.be**. "
"Never a copied value."
msgstr ""
"Le certificat **de votre établissement**, obtenu sur **ehealth.fgov.be**. "
"Jamais une valeur copiée."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Institution INAMI Number**"
msgstr "**Numéro INAMI de l'institution**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"Your institution's INAMI/RIZIV number, used in the STS, MDA, eFact and "
"eAgreement requests."
msgstr ""
"Le numéro INAMI/RIZIV de votre institution, utilisé dans les demandes STS, "
"MDA, eFact et eAgreement."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Your number**: 8 digits (institution) or 11 digits (NIHII-11)."
msgstr ""
"**Votre numéro** : 8 chiffres (institution) ou 11 chiffres (NIHII-11)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Competence Code**"
msgstr "**Code de compétence**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"The last 3 digits of the NIHII-11 (MR/MRS only, not CSJ); fallback when the "
"certified NIHII-11 cannot be read from the token."
msgstr ""
"Les 3 derniers chiffres du NIHII-11 (MR/MRS uniquement, pas CSJ) ; solution "
"de repli lorsque le NIHII-11 certifié ne peut être lu depuis le jeton."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**110** (MR) or **210** (some MRS)."
msgstr "**110** (MR) ou **210** (certaines MRS)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Legal Interest Rate (%)**"
msgstr "**Taux d'intérêt légal (%)**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"The annual Belgian legal rate used to calculate the late-payment interest an"
" insurer owes on a submission paid past the deadline."
msgstr ""
"Le taux légal belge annuel utilisé pour calculer les intérêts de retard "
"qu'une mutuelle doit sur un envoi payé hors délai."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "The **rate published for the year**; **0** disables the calculation."
msgstr "Le **taux publié pour l'année** ; **0** désactive le calcul."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Care Provider NIHII**"
msgstr "**NIHII du prestataire de soins**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"The **personal** NIHII-11 of the caregiver (nurse, physician) who issues the"
" MDA insurability requests — required by WalCareNet/MyCareNet."
msgstr ""
"Le NIHII-11 **personnel** du soignant (infirmier, médecin) qui émet les "
"demandes d'assurabilité MDA — requis par WalCareNet/MyCareNet."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "The NIHII of the **care provider at your establishment** (11 digits)."
msgstr ""
"Le NIHII du **prestataire de soins de votre établissement** (11 chiffres)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Environment**"
msgstr "**Environnement**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"*Acceptance* = test servers (simulated data); *Production* = real servers "
"(real billing)."
msgstr ""
"*Acceptation* = serveurs de test (données simulées) ; *Production* = "
"serveurs réels (facturation réelle)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"**Acceptance** as long as not validated, then **Production** after "
"accreditation."
msgstr ""
"**Acceptation** tant que non validé, puis **Production** après "
"accréditation."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Default Platform**"
msgstr "**Plateforme par défaut**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"The target network: WalCareNet (AViQ, Wallonia), MyCareNet (federal), "
"IrisCareNet (Brussels, MDA)."
msgstr ""
"Le réseau cible : WalCareNet (AViQ, Wallonie), MyCareNet (fédéral), "
"IrisCareNet (Bruxelles, MDA)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**WalCareNet** for a Walloon MR/MRS."
msgstr "**WalCareNet** pour une MR/MRS wallonne."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "**Stub Mode (Development)**"
msgstr "**Mode stub (développement)**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid "Simulates eHealth responses without a real call — for testing."
msgstr "Simule les réponses eHealth sans appel réel — pour les tests."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:43
msgid ""
"**Enabled** in test; **disabled** in production (requires a valid "
"certificate + CIN license)."
msgstr ""
"**Activé** en test ; **désactivé** en production (exige un certificat valide"
" + licence CIN)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "Start cautiously"
msgstr "Démarrer prudemment"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:71
msgid ""
"At start-up: **Acceptance + Stub Mode enabled**. You validate the whole flow"
" without sending anything real. Once accreditation is obtained, switch "
"**Stub Mode disabled**, then **Production**."
msgstr ""
"Au démarrage : **Acceptation + Mode stub activé**. Vous validez tout le flux"
" sans rien envoyer de réel. Une fois l'accréditation obtenue, passez **Mode "
"stub désactivé**, puis **Production**."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:76
msgid "eHealth Automation"
msgstr "Automatisation eHealth"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:78
msgid ""
"**Settings > Nursing Home > eHealth Automation.** The automatic behaviours "
"around insurability and logs."
msgstr ""
"**Réglages > Maison de repos > Automatisation eHealth.** Les comportements "
"automatiques autour de l'assurabilité et des journaux."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**Auto MDA Check**"
msgstr "**Contrôle MDA automatique**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"Automatically checks each resident's insurability before generating the "
"eFact — avoids rejections for invalid insurability (see "
"[MDA](../ehealth/mda.md))."
msgstr ""
"Vérifie automatiquement l'assurabilité de chaque résident avant de générer "
"l'eFact — évite les rejets pour assurabilité invalide (voir "
"[MDA](../ehealth/mda.md))."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**Enabled** as soon as the MDA is in production."
msgstr "**Activé** dès que le MDA est en production."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**Log Retention (days)**"
msgstr "**Conservation des journaux (jours)**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"Number of days communication and audit logs are kept; the oldest are purged "
"by the monthly cron."
msgstr ""
"Nombre de jours pendant lesquels les journaux de communication et d'audit "
"sont conservés ; les plus anciens sont purgés par le cron mensuel."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**2555** (7 years, Belgian legal requirement for health data)."
msgstr "**2555** (7 ans, obligation légale belge pour les données de santé)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**No-Facet Report Email**"
msgstr "**E-mail de signalement no-facet**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"Address used by the *Report to intermut* button on an MDA request that "
"remained \"no-facet\" (no insurer answered within 24 h) — to be escalated to"
" the CIN/intermut."
msgstr ""
"Adresse utilisée par le bouton *Signaler à l'intermut* sur une demande MDA "
"restée « no-facet » (aucune mutuelle n'a répondu dans les 24 h) — à "
"escalader vers le CIN/intermut."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "Leave the default **intermut** address."
msgstr "Laissez l'adresse **intermut** par défaut."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:87
msgid "Software Service Desk"
msgstr "Service Desk du logiciel"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:89
msgid ""
"**Settings > Nursing Home > Software Service Desk.** The **first point of "
"contact** when a provider has a problem — an AViQ accreditation requirement."
msgstr ""
"**Réglages > Maison de repos > Service Desk du logiciel.** Le **premier "
"point de contact** lorsqu'un prestataire rencontre un problème — une "
"exigence d'accréditation de l'AViQ."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**Service Desk Contact**"
msgstr "**Contact du Service Desk**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"The software publisher's contact (name, email, phone, logo), shown by the "
"*Contact LPLG* button on eAgreement requests."
msgstr ""
"Le contact de l'éditeur du logiciel (nom, e-mail, téléphone, logo), affiché "
"par le bouton *Contacter LPLG* sur les demandes eAgreement."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "Leave the default **LPLG contact**."
msgstr "Laissez le contact **LPLG** par défaut."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:96
msgid "eAgreement Responsible Practitioner"
msgstr "Praticien responsable eAgreement"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:98
msgid ""
"**Settings > Nursing Home > eAgreement Responsible Practitioner.** On an "
"[eAgreement](../ehealth/eagreement.md) request, the responsible practitioner"
" is the clinician who carried out the Katz assessment. If they have no "
"personal NIHII, the request borrows the identity of the head nurse, then of "
"the coordinating physician."
msgstr ""
"**Réglages > Maison de repos > Praticien responsable eAgreement.** Sur une "
"demande [eAgreement](../ehealth/eagreement.md), le praticien responsable est"
" le clinicien qui a réalisé l'évaluation Katz. S'il n'a pas de NIHII "
"personnel, la demande emprunte l'identité de l'infirmier en chef, puis du "
"médecin coordinateur."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**Head Nurse (NIHII fallback)**"
msgstr "**Infirmier en chef (repli NIHII)**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"Their NIHII identifies the responsible practitioner when the Katz assessor "
"(nurse, care assistant) has no NIHII."
msgstr ""
"Son NIHII identifie le praticien responsable lorsque l'évaluateur Katz "
"(infirmier, aide-soignant) n'a pas de NIHII."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "Fill in the establishment's **head nurse**."
msgstr "Renseignez l'**infirmier en chef** de l'établissement."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid "**Coordinating Physician (NIHII fallback)**"
msgstr "**Médecin coordinateur (repli NIHII)**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"Fallback when no nurse NIHII is available, and **mandatory** for a category "
"D Katz (physician required)."
msgstr ""
"Repli lorsqu'aucun NIHII d'infirmier n'est disponible, et **obligatoire** "
"pour un Katz de catégorie D (médecin requis)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:68
msgid ""
"Fill in the **coordinating physician** — essential for category D Katz."
msgstr ""
"Renseignez le **médecin coordinateur** — essentiel pour un Katz de catégorie"
" D."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid "The Katz category is for declaring, not for setting the amount"
msgstr "La catégorie Katz sert à déclarer, pas à fixer le montant"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:112
msgid ""
"The **dependency flat rate** is the **same amount** for all Katz categories "
"(AViQ tariffs); the category serves to **declare the resident's profile** to"
" the health insurance fund. A category **D** nonetheless requires a "
"**physician** as the eAgreement's responsible practitioner — hence the "
"importance of this field."
msgstr ""
"Le **forfait de dépendance** est le **même montant** pour toutes les "
"catégories Katz (tarifs AViQ) ; la catégorie sert à **déclarer le profil du "
"résident** à la mutuelle. Une catégorie **D** requiert néanmoins un "
"**médecin** comme praticien responsable de l'eAgreement — d'où l'importance "
"de ce champ."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:118
msgid "CIN Package License"
msgstr "Licence de package CIN"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:120
msgid ""
"**Settings > Nursing Home > CIN Package License.** The credentials that "
"authorise Resthome to send via GenAsync (eFact) and CommonInput (MDA)."
msgstr ""
"**Réglages > Maison de repos > Licence de package CIN.** Les identifiants "
"qui autorisent Resthome à envoyer via GenAsync (eFact) et CommonInput (MDA)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid "**Package License Username**"
msgstr "**Nom d'utilisateur de la licence de package**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid "Username of the software license, required for eFact and MDA."
msgstr ""
"Nom d'utilisateur de la licence logicielle, requis pour l'eFact et le MDA."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid ""
"Provided by the **CIN/NIC** at accreditation — specific to your software."
msgstr ""
"Fourni par le **CIN/NIC** lors de l'accréditation — spécifique à votre "
"logiciel."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid "**Package License Password**"
msgstr "**Mot de passe de la licence de package**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid "Password of the software license (masked field)."
msgstr "Mot de passe de la licence logicielle (champ masqué)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:109
msgid "Provided by the **CIN/NIC**; **secret**, do not disclose it."
msgstr "Fourni par le **CIN/NIC** ; **secret**, ne le divulguez pas."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:128
msgid "Where to obtain it"
msgstr "Où l'obtenir"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:131
msgid ""
"The Package License is issued by the **CIN/NIC** when the software is "
"accredited. It has **no default value**: as long as it is not configured "
"(and stub mode disabled), real submissions remain blocked."
msgstr ""
"La licence de package est délivrée par le **CIN/NIC** lors de "
"l'accréditation du logiciel. Elle n'a **aucune valeur par défaut** : tant "
"qu'elle n'est pas configurée (et le mode stub désactivé), les envois réels "
"restent bloqués."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:136
msgid "Account C (Wallonia)"
msgstr "Compte C (Wallonie)"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:138
msgid ""
"**Settings > MR/MRS > Account C (Wallonia).** Since the 6th State Reform, "
"the insurer pays the Walloon MR/MRS flat-rate fees to a dedicated "
"**financial account C**, declared to the CIN during eFact registration."
msgstr ""
"**Réglages > MR/MRS > Compte C (Wallonie).** Depuis la 6e réforme de l'État,"
" la mutuelle paie les forfaits de la MR/MRS wallonne sur un **compte "
"financier C** dédié, déclaré au CIN lors de l'enregistrement eFact."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:128
msgid "**Account C Bank Journal**"
msgstr "**Journal bancaire Compte C**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:128
msgid ""
"The bank journal of the Walloon account. The **IBAN** (ET 10 Z 45-47a) and "
"the **BIC** (Z 53-54a) written in the 920000 are derived from it."
msgstr ""
"Le journal bancaire du compte wallon. L'**IBAN** (ET 10 Z 45-47a) et le "
"**BIC** (Z 53-54a) inscrits dans le 920000 en sont dérivés."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:128
msgid ""
"Your establishment's **Account C journal**. Fill in the IBAN on the bank "
"account and the BIC on the bank."
msgstr ""
"Le **journal Compte C** de votre établissement. Renseignez l'IBAN sur le "
"compte bancaire et le BIC sur la banque."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid "Otherwise, WalCareNet rejection"
msgstr "Sinon, rejet WalCareNet"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:149
msgid ""
"Without a valid Account C, WalCareNet **rejects the batch**: **104511** "
"(missing IBAN) or **105311** (missing BIC). The IBAN and BIC shown under the"
" field are read-only — they come from the journal's bank account. See [eFact"
" Rejections](../ehealth/efact-rejets.md)."
msgstr ""
"Sans Compte C valide, WalCareNet **rejette le lot** : **104511** (IBAN "
"manquant) ou **105311** (BIC manquant). L'IBAN et le BIC affichés sous le "
"champ sont en lecture seule — ils proviennent du compte bancaire du journal."
" Voir [Rejets eFact](../ehealth/efact-rejets.md)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:155
msgid "eFact Header"
msgstr "En-tête eFact"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:157
msgid ""
"**Settings > MR/MRS > eFact Header.** The header information carried by each"
" [eFact](../ehealth/efact.md) 920000 message (segment 300)."
msgstr ""
"**Réglages > MR/MRS > En-tête eFact.** Les informations d'en-tête portées "
"par chaque message [eFact](../ehealth/efact.md) 920000 (segment 300)."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid "**eFact Contact Person**"
msgstr "**Personne de contact eFact**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid ""
"Name and phone written in the header (Z305 surname / Z306 first name / Z307 "
"phone) — the person an insurer contacts for a billing question."
msgstr ""
"Nom et téléphone inscrits dans l'en-tête (Z305 nom / Z306 prénom / Z307 "
"téléphone) — la personne qu'une mutuelle contacte pour une question de "
"facturation."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid ""
"For example, the establishment's **director**. If empty, the establishment "
"name is used."
msgstr ""
"Par exemple, le **directeur** de l'établissement. Si vide, le nom de "
"l'établissement est utilisé."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid "**eFact Invoice Type (Z308)**"
msgstr "**Type de facture eFact (Z308)**"

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid ""
"The Z308 \"invoice type\" zone: 01 Hospitalisation, 03 Ambulatory, 09 Mixed."
msgstr ""
"La zone Z308 « type de facture » : 01 Hospitalisation, 03 Ambulatoire, 09 "
"Mixte."

#: ../../content/configuration/reglages-ehealth.md:146
msgid ""
"**01** by default (accepted at the 931000 check). Only switch to **03** if "
"AViQ/CIN confirms it."
msgstr ""
"**01** par défaut (accepté au contrôle 931000). Ne passez à **03** que si "
"l'AViQ/CIN le confirme."

